{"tid":2123974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"123宗確診「三連破」 主婦患者增  街市高危 張竹君籲少買餸","createTime":"2020-07-25T05:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T06:53:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"04397d72672bacc082500f96efc8f25ef7111fe7","tid":2123974,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:17:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200725/Y7FSL6HWSPFVTUBL4QHZNA4Z74/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200725%2FY7FSL6HWSPFVTUBL4QHZNA4Z74%2F&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=b5448eb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200725%2FY7FSL6HWSPFVTUBL4QHZNA4Z74%2F&h=f2de8ee6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200725/Y7FSL6HWSPFVTUBL4QHZNA4Z74/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n123宗確診「三連破」 主婦患者增 <br />\n街市高危 張竹君籲少買餸<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎確診連續三日破百，初步確診個案亦約100宗。政府禁止晚市堂食後，市民多購買餸菜自煮，但公眾街市亦爆發疫情。衞生防護中心指出，源頭不明個案患者多是負責買餸的家庭主婦及長者，人多擠迫的街市懷疑是傳播病毒的高危地點，呼籲減少去街市，又或一次多買幾日餸。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：入境處工會主席三消防中招<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Q0EIZ45x2jYmTQ9VIzEoKwyOGNo=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T24R4KXARW2BQOZ7W6NZN4BZJY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQ0EIZ45x2jYmTQ9VIzEoKwyOGNo%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT24R4KXARW2BQOZ7W6NZN4BZJY.jpg&h=9794b8b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅磡街市爆疫，昨日來買餸的市民戴口罩及眼罩自保。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心昨日公佈，本港新增123宗確診個案，其中115宗為本地個案，兩者都是連續三日創新高，另外約有100宗初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n紅磡街市累計六人染疫<br />\n<br />\n當中三宗個案與街市有關，紅磡街市一名清潔工（第2,341號個案）及賣乾貨檔販（第2,316號個案）確診，兩人先後本月16及19日病發。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，紅磡街市涉及六名確診病人，包括一名凍肉店員工，最早於18日確診；。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n115宗屬本地個案中，53宗源頭未明。衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君指出，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n現時社區隱形患者和病毒量較多，人多聚集容易受感染。「街市好逼好多人，環境未必通風得好好，。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n多名身穿保護衣物的食環署清潔工人昨到紅磡街市大清洗。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民：雪櫃空間有限<br />\n<br />\n多名到紅磡街市的市民稱，街市的菜、魚較為新鮮，故習慣到街市購買餸。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n關女士則稱自疫症爆發，每次買餸都會買兩至三天的份量，但家中的雪櫃空間有限，。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d5db17185fb247f1636e980f39f7e8b7fd077860","tid":2123974,"uid":340796,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:20:25.000Z","msg":"街市真心危險<br />\n廢老比例又高<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"749dea60e40ed9c6c0c9798b91b7773a3dab4c4b","tid":2123974,"uid":169071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"之前又話可以揾到源頭，原來用排除法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揾到未呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n垃圾政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae8d5a25edb0c9f40168935eb70b4af4496b43b","tid":2123974,"uid":60527,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:30:57.000Z","msg":"禁堂食，禁買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光合作用？"},{"pid":"7ac3aa0b4cca8008f1fce2b807b15d3141086b26","tid":2123974,"uid":33456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1ae8d5a25edb0c9f40168935eb70b4af4496b43b","tid":2123974,"uid":60527,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:30:57.000Z","msg":"禁堂食，禁買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光合作用？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:32:30.000Z","msg":"學支那咁囉&hellip;糧食配給專人送上門<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c85b08247fc53efa402d13aed3a3aa743f3cb86c","tid":2123974,"uid"